msgstr "&i18n-pimsettingexporter; kasutamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:64
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Backing up is an essential practice for all users. &i18n-"
#| "pimsettingexporter; is a great tool for backing up or moving all of your "
#| "settings and email to a new installation. You also use &i18n-"
#| "pimsettingexporter; to import previous backups."
msgid ""
"Backing up is an essential practice for all users. &i18n-pimdataexporter; is "
"a great tool for backing up or moving all of your settings and email to a "
"new installation. You also use &i18n-pimdataexporter; to import previous "
"backups."
msgstr ""
"Varundamine on äärmiselt oluline kõigile kasutajatele. &i18n-"
"pimsettingexporter; on suurepärane tööriist kõigi sinu seadistuste ja "
"kirjade varundamisel või liigutamisel uude süsteemi. Samuti saab &i18n-"
"pimsettingexporter;t kasutada varasemate varukoopiate importimiseks."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:67
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can use <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Export "
#| "&kmail; Data...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> through the message view "
#| "window or &i18n-pimsettingexporter; can be run as a standalone "
#| "application by running &i18n-pimsettingexporter; in the application "
#| "launcher."
msgid ""
"You can use <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Export &kmail; "
"Data...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> through the message view window or &i18n-"
"pimdataexporter; can be run as a standalone application by running &i18n-"
"pimdataexporter; in the application launcher."
msgstr ""
"Võib valida menüükäsu <menuchoice><guimenu>Tööriistad</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Ekspordi &kmail;i andmed...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"kirjade vaate aknas, aga &i18n-pimsettingexporter; võib käivitada ka "
"iseseisvalt, kui valida rakenduste käivitajas &i18n-pimsettingexporter;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To perform a backup, <action>select <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Back Up Data...</guimenuitem></menuchoice></action>, it "
"will prompt you to close all kdepim applications. <warning><para>Make sure "
"you close all windows, data loss is possible if you don't.</para></warning> "
"Once you have closed them, click <guibutton>Yes</guibutton> to continue, or "
"<guibutton>No</guibutton> to cancel."
msgstr ""
"Varundamiseks <action>vali <menuchoice><guimenu>Fail</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Varunda andmed...</guimenuitem></menuchoice></action>, "
"mille järel palutakse sulgeda kõik KDE-PIM-i aknad. "
"<warning><para>Kontrolli, et oleksid sulgenud kõik aknad, sest muidu võivad "
"andmed kaotsi minna.</para></warning> Kui oled aknad sulgenud, klõpsa nupule "
"<guibutton>Jah</guibutton> jätkamiseks või <guibutton>Ei</guibutton> "
"loobumiseks."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You will be prompted to create a backup name, enter the name into the "
"<guilabel>File</guilabel> textbox, &eg; <replaceable>mymailsettings</"
"replaceable>. The default filetype it saves as is <filename role=\"extension"
"\">.zip</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Sul palutakse määrata varukoopia nimi. Kirjuta see tekstikasti "
"<guilabel>Fail</guilabel> (&eg; <replaceable>minukirjadeseadistused</"
"replaceable>). Vaikimisi salvestatakse fail laiendiga <filename role="
"\"extension\">.zip</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The next screen will allow you to select what you wish to backup, by default "
"everything is selected."
msgstr ""
"Järgmisel ekraanil saad valida, mida varundada. Vaikimisi on valitud kõik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmail; Mails selection will only backup mails in your <quote>Local Folders</"
"quote>, it will backup &imap; settings and download messages upon restore. "
"If you have emails on a &imap; server you wish to be backed up, you should "
"use <ulink url=\"help:/akonadi_folderarchive_agent\">Folder Archive Agent</"
"ulink> to archive those emails to a local folder."
msgstr ""
"&kmail;i kirjade valimine varundab ainult <quote>kohalikes kaustades</quote> "
"leiduvad kirjad. &imap; seadistused salvestatakse samuti ning kirjad "
"laaditakse alla taastamise järel. Kui sul on kirju &imap; serveris, mida "
"soovid varundada, tuleks nende arhiveerimiseks kohalikku kausta kasutada "
"<ulink url=\"help:/akonadi_folderarchive_agent\">kausta arhiveerimise "
"agenti</ulink>."

