#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The final screen shows the log of the backup up process. You can close the "
"window once you have reviewed the log and verified your backup was "
"successful."
msgstr ""
"Viimane ekraan näitab varundamise logi. Selle võib sulgeda, kui oled logi "
"üle vaadanud ja veendunud, et varundamine kulges edukalt."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To restore your backup, select <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Restore Data...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> within "
#| "&i18n-pimsettingexporter;."
msgid ""
"To restore your backup, select <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Restore Data...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> within &i18n-"
"pimdataexporter;."
msgstr ""
"Varukoopia taastamiseks vali &i18n-pimsettingexporter;s "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Fail</guimenu><guimenuitem>Taasta andmed...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Archive "
"Information</guimenuitem></menuchoice> you can select a backup archive and "
"view its content."
msgstr ""
"Menüükäsuga <menuchoice><guimenu>Tööriistad</guimenu><guimenuitem>Näita "
"arhiivi teavet</guimenuitem></menuchoice> saab valida varundatud arhiivi ja "
"näha selle sisu."

